      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The SST k-omega turbulence model is the FDA-recommended approach for rotary blood pump CFD per the 2017 FDA guidance. Model form selection is supported by published benchmark comparisons (FDA critical path pump study) and is appropriate for this risk level."
